[0m[49m[39m  1399, 1399[0m:[39m[49m **FDA-strategy artifact with regulatory-counsel review.** The institutional regulatory positioning is documented, reviewed by FDA-experienced regulatory counsel, and maintained as the deployment evolves. Architectural changes affecting regulatory positioning are reviewed against the artifact.
